text: Michal Baldrián (born 16 February 1970) is a Czech former cyclist. He competed in the individual pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Czechoslovakia Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
